\begin_layout Standard
State and microregion classes represent the places where production units
 are located, allowing to define the state and the microregion for the farms
 and plants related with sugar-cane, currently the SustenAgro system has
 7 states that belong to the center-south of Brazil and 243 microregions
 within the registered states, these data were semantically queried and
 integrated in the system from a query on DBpedia.
 
\end_layout

